{"id":166,"parent_id":158,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":166,"title":"2 Corinthians 8","subtitle":"","short_title":"2 Cor.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/8","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 8"],[".studySummary",["i","True Saints impart of their substance to the poor—Christ, out of His poverty, brought eternal riches."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/8.1","order":"03.10.008.18920"},["b","1"],"Moreover, brethren,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"we"],"do you to wit of the grace of God bestowed on the churches of Macedonia;"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/8.2","order":"03.10.008.18921"},["b","2"],"How that in a great",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"trial"],"of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"affliction"],"the abundance of their joy and their deep",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_2c"},"poverty"],"abounded unto the riches of their",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_2d"},"liberality"],"."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/8.3","order":"03.10.008.18922"},["b","3"],"For to",["i","their"],"power, I bear record, yea, and beyond",["i","their"],"power",["i","they were"],"willing of themselves;"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/8.4","order":"03.10.008.18923"},["b","4"],"Praying us with much entreaty that we would receive the gift, and",["i","take upon us"],"the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"fellowship"],"of the ministering to the saints."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/8.5","order":"03.10.008.18924"},["b","5"],"And",["i","this they did,"],"not as we hoped, but first",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"gave"],"their own selves to the Lord, and unto us by the will of God."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/8.6","order":"03.10.008.18925"},["b","6"],"Insomuch that we desired Titus, that as he had begun, so he would also finish in you the same grace also."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/8.7","order":"03.10.008.18926"},["b","7"],"Therefore, as ye abound in every",["i","thing, in"],"faith, and utterance, and knowledge, and",["i","in"],"all",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"diligence"],", and",["i","in"],"your love to us,",["i","see"],"that ye abound in this grace also."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/8.8","order":"03.10.008.18927"},["b","8"],"I speak",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"not"],"by commandment, but by occasion of the forwardness of others, and to prove the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"sincerity"],"of your love."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/8.9","order":"03.10.008.18928"},["b","9"],"For ye know the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"grace"],"of our Lord Jesus Christ, that, though he was",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"rich"],", yet for your sakes he became",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_9c"},"poor"],", that ye through his",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_9d"},"poverty"],"might be rich."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/8.10","order":"03.10.008.18929"},["b","10"],"And herein I give",["i","my"],"advice: for this is expedient for you, who have begun before, not only to do, but also to be forward a year ago."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/8.11","order":"03.10.008.18930"},["b","11"],"Now therefore perform the doing",["i","of it;"],"that as",["i","there was"],"a readiness to will, so",["i","there may be"],"a performance also out of that which ye have."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/8.12","order":"03.10.008.18931"},["b","12"],"For if there be first a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"willing"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"mind"],",",["i","it is"],"accepted according to that a man hath,",["i","and"],"not according to that he hath not."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/8.13","order":"03.10.008.18932"},["b","13"],"For",["i","I mean"],"not that other men be eased, and ye burdened:"],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/8.14","order":"03.10.008.18933"},["b","14"],"But by an equality,",["i","that"],"now at this time your abundance",["i","may be a supply"],"for their want, that their",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"abundance"],"also may be",["i","a supply"],"for your want: that there may be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"equality"],":"],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/8.15","order":"03.10.008.18934"},["b","15"],"As it is written, He that",["i","had",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"gathered"]],"much had nothing over; and he that",["i","had gathered"],"little had no lack."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/8.16","order":"03.10.008.18935"},["b","16"],"But thanks",["i","be"],"to God, which put the same earnest care into the heart of Titus for you."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/8.17","order":"03.10.008.18936"},["b","17"],"For indeed he accepted the exhortation; but being more forward, of his own accord he went unto you."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/8.18","order":"03.10.008.18937"},["b","18"],"And we have sent with him the brother, whose praise",["i","is"],"in the gospel throughout all the churches;"],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/8.19","order":"03.10.008.18938"},["b","19"],"And not",["i","that"],"only, but who was also chosen of the churches to travel with us with this grace, which is administered by us to the glory of the same Lord, and",["i","declaration of"],"your ready mind:"],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/8.20","order":"03.10.008.18939"},["b","20"],"Avoiding this, that no man should blame us in this abundance which is administered by us:"],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/8.21","order":"03.10.008.18940"},["b","21"],"Providing for",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"honest"],"things, not only in the sight of the Lord, but also in the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_21b"},"sight"],"of men."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/8.22","order":"03.10.008.18941"},["b","22"],"And we have sent with them our brother, whom we have oftentimes proved diligent in many things, but now much more diligent, upon the great",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"confidence"],"which",["i","I have"],"in you."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/8.23","order":"03.10.008.18942"},["b","23"],"Whether",["i","any do inquire"],"of Titus,",["i","he is"],"my partner and fellowhelper concerning you: or our brethren",["i","be inquired of, they are"],"the messengers of the churches,",["i","and"],"the glory of Christ."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/8.24","order":"03.10.008.18943"},["b","24"],"Wherefore shew ye to them, and before the churches, the proof of your love, and of our boasting on your behalf."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/8.1a","order":"03.10.008.18944"},["b","1a"],["span.small","GR"],"we make known (or declare) to you the grace."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/8.2a","order":"03.10.008.18946"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/probation"},"TG Probation"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/test"},"Test"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/8.2b","order":"03.10.008.18948"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/affliction"},"TG Affliction"],"."],["div",{"id":"2c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/8.2c","order":"03.10.008.18950"},["b","2c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/mark/12.44.43-44"},"Mark 12:44 (43–44)"],"."],["div",{"id":"2d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/8.2d","order":"03.10.008.18952"},["b","2d"],["span.small","GR"],"sincerity, purity of mind.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/generosity"},"TG Generosity"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/8.4a","order":"03.10.008.18954"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/88.133"},"D&C 88:133"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/8.5a","order":"03.10.008.18956"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/self-sacrifice"},"TG Self-Sacrifice"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/8.7a","order":"03.10.008.18958"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/diligence"},"TG Diligence"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/8.8a","order":"03.10.008.18960"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/63.22"},"D&C 63:22"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/8.8b","order":"03.10.008.18962"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sincere"},"TG Sincere"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/8.9a","order":"03.10.008.18964"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/grace"},"TG Grace"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/8.9b","order":"03.10.008.18966"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/treasure"},"TG Treasure"],"."],["div",{"id":"9c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/8.9c","order":"03.10.008.18968"},["b","9c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.7.5-8"},"Philip. 2:7 (5–8)"],"."],["div",{"id":"9d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/8.9d","order":"03.10.008.18970"},["b","9d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/6.10"},"2 Cor. 6:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/8.12a","order":"03.10.008.18972"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/25.2.1-7"},"Ex. 25:2 (1–7)"],"."],["div",{"id":"12b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/8.12b","order":"03.10.008.18974"},["b","12b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/64.34"},"D&C 64:34"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/8.14a","order":"03.10.008.18976"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/1.30.29-30"},"Alma 1:30 (29–30)"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/8.14b","order":"03.10.008.18978"},["b","14b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/consecration"},"TG Consecration"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/8.15a","order":"03.10.008.18980"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/16.18"},"Ex. 16:18"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/8.21a","order":"03.10.008.18982"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/honesty"},"TG Honesty"],"."],["div",{"id":"21b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/8.21b","order":"03.10.008.18984"},["b","21b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/12.17"},"Rom. 12:17"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/8.22a","order":"03.10.008.18986"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/2.3"},"2 Cor. 2:3"],"."]]}
